Three (3) years of experience developing programs in at least one of the following programming languages: Python, R, C, C++, or SAS;
Demonstrated experience creating analytic or software products, working across development lifecycle stages including requirements analysis, design& development, testing, deployment and maintenance;
Demonstrated experience programming in SQL and practical application of the following SQL techniques:
